<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="278800000t" end="304000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">不用怕，我們就當玩捉迷藏吧</p>
<p begin="376800000t" end="386800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">起來</p>
<p begin="453600000t" end="502800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">自由這東西非常可貴，也相當殘酷</p>
<p begin="595200000t" end="641200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">「約定的夢幻島 S2」</p>
<p begin="663200000t" end="702000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">(回想起來了　回想起來了)</p>
<p begin="702800000t" end="741600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">(在那一眨眼間的絕望感覺)</p>
<p begin="742400000t" end="782000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">(即使醒來了　仍然在夢中)</p>
<p begin="782800000t" end="824800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(夢見我們剎那光輝的故事)</p>
<p begin="825600000t" end="867600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(時鐘的秒針)</p>
<p begin="868400000t" end="897600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">(請對我報以微笑吧)</p>
<p begin="898400000t" end="957200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">(滿腦子心心念念的都是你啊)</p>
<p begin="982800000t" end="1021600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">(打破冰封三尺的明日吧)</p>
<p begin="1022400000t" end="1062800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(盡是些絕對不能失去的事物)</p>
<p begin="1063600000t" end="1102000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(我在命運指引的前路上找到了你)</p>
<p begin="1102800000t" end="1140400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(如今眼淚已再也沒有意義)</p>
<p begin="1141200000t" end="1180000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(在飛快地運轉的世界一角)</p>
<p begin="1180800000t" end="1221600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">(有如吶喊一樣呼吸著)</p>
<p begin="1222400000t" end="1261600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">(如能在跨越千千萬萬時光後重逢)</p>
<p begin="1262400000t" end="1307590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">(就在絕望的前方一步笑吧)</p>
<p begin="1606400000t" end="1628400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">你們看，外面的世界</p>
<p begin="1629200000t" end="1649600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">所有東西都是這麼大的</p>
<p begin="1650400000t" end="1683600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">這裡跟剛才的森林是完全不同的</p>
<p begin="1697200000t" end="1722400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">這些蟲子好像在哪裡看過</p>
<p begin="1761200000t" end="1773200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">等等我</p>
<p begin="1790800000t" end="1802000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">好了…</p>
<p begin="1802800000t" end="1823600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">托馬　　拉尼恩</p>
<p begin="1926400000t" end="1948400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">這樣吧，大家靠在一起走</p>
<p begin="1951200000t" end="1972000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">我們不知道前面會遇上甚麼</p>
<p begin="1972800000t" end="1999600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">農場說不定已經派人來追截我們</p>
<p begin="2031200000t" end="2064400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">不可以一次喝太多水和吃太多食物</p>
<p begin="2065200000t" end="2081600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">大家都要儘量節省物資</p>
<p begin="2082400000t" end="2100800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">儲糧才能維持更久</p>
<p begin="2101600000t" end="2112000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">知道…</p>
<p begin="2232400000t" end="2245200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">不用擔心</p>
<p begin="2246000000t" end="2274000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">這裡不像是野獸棲息的地方</p>
<p begin="2286800000t" end="2302000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">我找不到任何腳印</p>
<p begin="2302800000t" end="2323600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">爪痕及糞便的痕跡</p>
<p begin="2330800000t" end="2345600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">就當是玩捉迷藏吧</p>
<p begin="2361200000t" end="2383600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">艾瑪，你別硬撐</p>
<p begin="2388000000t" end="2410400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">讓我來看守，你休息一下吧</p>
<p begin="2450400000t" end="2462000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">謝謝你</p>
<p begin="2532000000t" end="2549600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">對不起，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="2568000000t" end="2588800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">當初如果不是因為我</p>
<p begin="2596000000t" end="2628800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">你的手和耳朵或許不會受傷</p>
<p begin="2654000000t" end="2670800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">不要緊，小事而已</p>
<p begin="2671600000t" end="2694400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">看到你的笑容，就知道你沒事</p>
<p begin="2695200000t" end="2707200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">這樣就夠了</p>
<p begin="2750800000t" end="2761200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">謝謝你</p>
<p begin="2802400000t" end="2833200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">艾瑪，我要生存下去</p>
<p begin="2839200000t" end="2853600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">我要守護我的家人</p>
<p begin="2860400000t" end="2886800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">我要守護你和所有家人</p>
<p begin="2896000000t" end="2931200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">我現在就在這裡發誓</p>
<p begin="2937600000t" end="2968800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">無論如何，我都不會再跟你們分開</p>
<p begin="2977200000t" end="2987600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">雷</p>
<p begin="2994000000t" end="3012000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">別獨自承擔所有責任</p>
<p begin="3053200000t" end="3073200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">對了，接下來要做甚麼</p>
<p begin="3076000000t" end="3095200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">首先要尋找食水</p>
<p begin="3096000000t" end="3114000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">之前不是看到一條河流嗎</p>
<p begin="3114800000t" end="3132800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">看看河水能否飲用吧</p>
<p begin="3133600000t" end="3158000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">你說得對，首先是水</p>
<p begin="3161200000t" end="3187600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">如果找到河流，多數就會找到食物</p>
<p begin="3205600000t" end="3234400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">不過我擔心我們這麼想的話</p>
<p begin="3235200000t" end="3254000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">敵人也一樣會想到</p>
<p begin="3254800000t" end="3271200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">艾瑪、雷</p>
<p begin="3288800000t" end="3299200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">接下來要怎麼做</p>
<p begin="3300000000t" end="3318400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">知道要朝哪個方向走了嗎</p>
<p begin="3322800000t" end="3342800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">知道了，向東南方走</p>
<p begin="3346000000t" end="3378000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">東南方？　　就是東和南之間</p>
<p begin="3382400000t" end="3405200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">吉爾妲，我當然知道</p>
<p begin="3414800000t" end="3425200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">對了，雷</p>
<p begin="3441200000t" end="3470800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">這件東西是諾曼留下來的</p>
<p begin="3484000000t" end="3514000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">難道是威廉米涅瓦先生的</p>
<p begin="3519600000t" end="3530400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">沒錯</p>
<p begin="3531200000t" end="3559600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">我想一定是米涅瓦先生指引著我們</p>
<p begin="3665600000t" end="3676800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">這是甚麼</p>
<p begin="3680400000t" end="3717200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">B0114，是我們現在的位置</p>
<p begin="3719200000t" end="3733200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">現在的位置？</p>
<p begin="3742000000t" end="3754000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">就是說…</p>
<p begin="3781200000t" end="3826800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">B01…14，就是現在的位置</p>
<p begin="3891200000t" end="3918800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">這條線暗藏著摩斯密碼</p>
<p begin="3934400000t" end="3992400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">T、O、U、C、H、M、E</p>
<p begin="4004800000t" end="4020400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">就是說「觸摸我」</p>
<p begin="4072000000t" end="4094400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">這些不是摩斯密碼</p>
<p begin="4095200000t" end="4118800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">沒錯，孤兒院圖書館內</p>
<p begin="4119600000t" end="4132400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">有貓頭鷹印記的書</p>
<p begin="4133200000t" end="4147600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">其實有很多本</p>
<p begin="4154400000t" end="4180000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">當中只有一本沒有摩斯密碼</p>
<p begin="4187200000t" end="4216000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">那本就是神話書了　　神話？</p>
<p begin="4234400000t" end="4258800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">這本書就是這枝筆的密碼書</p>
<p begin="4264000000t" end="4292400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">是可以解開暗號的鎖匙</p>
<p begin="4300800000t" end="4317200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">這些是暗號</p>
<p begin="4318000000t" end="4343200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">輸入了答案，就會去下一關</p>
<p begin="4348800000t" end="4386000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">第13頁，第18行，第2個單字</p>
<p begin="4463200000t" end="4472000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">「Human」</p>
<p begin="4538800000t" end="4564000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">「如果需要我的幫忙，就來找我」</p>
<p begin="4564800000t" end="4604800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">「我的所在地點就在B0632」</p>
<p begin="4605600000t" end="4621200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">「威廉米涅瓦」</p>
<p begin="4658400000t" end="4691200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">我們要感謝諾曼把這枝筆留給我們</p>
<p begin="4696400000t" end="4703600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">對</p>
<p begin="4725200000t" end="4745200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">我很掛念諾曼</p>
<p begin="4751600000t" end="4766400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">馬克也掛念</p>
<p begin="4781600000t" end="4803600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">我也很掛念諾曼　　我也很掛念他</p>
<p begin="4804400000t" end="4836800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">希望可以再見到他…</p>
<p begin="4873600000t" end="4895200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">大家聽好了，你們都垂頭喪氣</p>
<p begin="4896000000t" end="4915600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">諾曼知道了一定會取笑我們</p>
<p begin="4916400000t" end="4954800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">說得對，你們聽到了吧　　聽到…</p>
<p begin="5020800000t" end="5030800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">伊蓓特</p>
<p begin="5031600000t" end="5066400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">安娜，我以前見過這些東西</p>
<p begin="5072400000t" end="5095200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">這些是甚麼</p>
<p begin="5112800000t" end="5123200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">我想起來了</p>
<p begin="5124000000t" end="5154400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">我在孤兒院看書時見過這種植物</p>
<p begin="5164400000t" end="5186400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">那本書好像是…</p>
<p begin="5187200000t" end="5209600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">《烏戈冒險記》　　對</p>
<p begin="5222000000t" end="5250000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">沒錯，那本書的確有提及這種植物</p>
<p begin="5250800000t" end="5265200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">它裡面充滿…</p>
<p begin="5268800000t" end="5281600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">一起說</p>
<p begin="5282400000t" end="5294800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">水…</p>
<p begin="5295600000t" end="5320000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">對，這種植物能夠儲水</p>
<p begin="5320800000t" end="5333200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">它的名字是海葵</p>
<p begin="5354800000t" end="5383600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">如果書本說得對，這些水可以飲用</p>
<p begin="5388800000t" end="5418000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">那我們就不用特地去尋找河流了</p>
<p begin="5418800000t" end="5454400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">太好了…</p>
<p begin="5488800000t" end="5500400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">如果是這樣</p>
<p begin="5501200000t" end="5521200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">就是這個森林和那些蟲子</p>
<p begin="5523600000t" end="5545200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">都在《烏戈冒險記》中出現過</p>
<p begin="5557200000t" end="5567200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">難道…</p>
<p begin="5568000000t" end="5600400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">難道這本書是外面世界的指南</p>
<p begin="5602800000t" end="5615200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">有可能是的</p>
<p begin="5620400000t" end="5648400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">你還記得摩斯密碼的意思嗎</p>
<p begin="5652400000t" end="5664800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">是約定？</p>
<p begin="5667600000t" end="5684000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">說不定這本書</p>
<p begin="5684800000t" end="5714400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">是米涅瓦先生跟我們締結的約定</p>
<p begin="5718800000t" end="5757200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">米涅瓦先生很有可能正在守護我們</p>
<p begin="5764800000t" end="5794400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">我覺得外面的世界雖然很危險</p>
<p begin="5795200000t" end="5814000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">但我們並非獨自一人</p>
<p begin="5818000000t" end="5850800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">我們有家人，也有同伴</p>
<p begin="5858800000t" end="5890400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">大家一起努力，跟米涅瓦先生見面</p>
<p begin="5892800000t" end="5912800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">讓我們結識更多新同伴</p>
<p begin="5913600000t" end="5932800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">再一起去接菲爾他們吧</p>
<p begin="5933600000t" end="5950800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">好…</p>
<p begin="6063400000t" end="6083800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">找到方向了嗎</p>
<p begin="6084600000t" end="6104200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">東南方一直走</p>
<p begin="6324600000t" end="6337000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">雷，怎麼了</p>
<p begin="6479400000t" end="6491400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">快點關燈</p>
<p begin="6581400000t" end="6611400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">大家快跑　　快跑，快點</p>
<p begin="6661800000t" end="6685400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">不用怕，我們就當玩捉迷藏吧</p>
<p begin="6709400000t" end="6719400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">起來</p>
<p begin="6951000000t" end="6987000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">無法選擇嗎？來吧，過來這邊吧</p>
<p begin="7023000000t" end="7052600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">好吧，所有人向前一直走</p>
<p begin="7056200000t" end="7066600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">看到嗎</p>
<p begin="7067400000t" end="7085800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">吉爾妲將運動能力弱的小孩</p>
<p begin="7086600000t" end="7099800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">集合起來</p>
<p begin="7102200000t" end="7120200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">剛才發訊號的是唐</p>
<p begin="7122200000t" end="7138600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">一定是他想出來的方法</p>
<p begin="7155000000t" end="7169400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">你們不用擔心</p>
<p begin="7171400000t" end="7196600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">我們一定會想到辦法對付那隻鬼</p>
<p begin="7198600000t" end="7209000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">小心</p>
<p begin="7231800000t" end="7247000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">那些是甚麼</p>
<p begin="7247800000t" end="7273000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">是陷阱，《烏戈冒險記》有提及過</p>
<p begin="7302200000t" end="7319000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">阿爾瓦皮聶拉之蛇…</p>
<p begin="7323000000t" end="7359800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">對，如果掉下去，就無法爬上來</p>
<p begin="7381800000t" end="7399800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">真的太好了，有辦法</p>
<p begin="7415000000t" end="7433400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">引敵人掉進陷阱就行了</p>
<p begin="7437000000t" end="7457800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">我明白了，那我倆去…</p>
<p begin="7458600000t" end="7476200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">不，我獨自去就行了</p>
<p begin="7477000000t" end="7504200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">你說甚麼？這樣可不行</p>
<p begin="7505000000t" end="7516200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">我可以的</p>
<p begin="7523000000t" end="7536600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">我不是因為太危險</p>
<p begin="7537400000t" end="7558200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">而寧願一個人去犧牲</p>
<p begin="7561400000t" end="7587800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">是因為我一個人也應付得來</p>
<p begin="7597400000t" end="7614600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">對了，你說我和你</p>
<p begin="7615400000t" end="7633800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">誰更擅長玩捉迷藏</p>
<p begin="7647800000t" end="7655400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">是你</p>
<p begin="7656200000t" end="7678600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">沒錯，那就交給我吧</p>
<p begin="7681400000t" end="7695800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">你跟吉爾妲他們會合</p>
<p begin="7696600000t" end="7708200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">順著風向走吧</p>
<p begin="7711800000t" end="7727800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">去吧　　好吧</p>
<p begin="7779800000t" end="7798200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">來吧，這邊</p>
<p begin="7817000000t" end="7825800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">對</p>
<p begin="7833000000t" end="7842600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">來吧</p>
<p begin="8014200000t" end="8029000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">已經找到了</p>
<p begin="8060600000t" end="8074200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">怎麼樣</p>
<p begin="8075000000t" end="8093800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">這東西根本不能吃</p>
<p begin="8094600000t" end="8115000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">因為它沒有人類的氣味</p>
<p begin="8135000000t" end="8170600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">我知道你在附近，你可以出來了</p>
<p begin="8171400000t" end="8205000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">你剛才很危險，不過沒事了</p>
<p begin="8208200000t" end="8224600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">現在已經安全</p>
<p begin="8225400000t" end="8246200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">怪物已經被我們殺了</p>
<p begin="8247000000t" end="8262600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">你可以出來了</p>
<p begin="8281400000t" end="8297000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">你獨自一人嗎</p>
<p begin="8297800000t" end="8318200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">其他小孩怎麼樣</p>
<p begin="8327000000t" end="8364600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">你應該明白不可能在外面生存</p>
<p begin="8365400000t" end="8386600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">還是跟我們回去吧</p>
<p begin="8387400000t" end="8402600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">讓我把他拉出來吧</p>
<p begin="8405800000t" end="8426600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">不用，你退到一旁</p>
<p begin="8439800000t" end="8453400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">你們來晚了</p>
<p begin="8457000000t" end="8486200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">因為所有人都死光了</p>
<p begin="8487000000t" end="8521400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">果然是你，81194，頂級品</p>
<p begin="8522200000t" end="8533800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">捉住他</p>
<p begin="8589800000t" end="8613400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">這是甚麼聲音</p>
<p begin="8654200000t" end="8668200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">我想沒事吧</p>
<p begin="8683000000t" end="8703400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">為何雷還沒回來</p>
<p begin="8705800000t" end="8722600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">不知道他是否有事</p>
<p begin="8725400000t" end="8740200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">應該沒事的</p>
<p begin="8753000000t" end="8779800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">艾瑪　　可能孤兒院派人追來</p>
<p begin="8889800000t" end="8933000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">艾瑪，你沒事吧？你的臉色變了</p>
<p begin="8939400000t" end="8961400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">我沒事，謝謝你</p>
<p begin="8965800000t" end="8982600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">我去看看，很快就回來</p>
<p begin="8993400000t" end="9015400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">大家順著風向繼續走吧</p>
<p begin="9020200000t" end="9032600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">我們知道了</p>
<p begin="9049400000t" end="9066200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">好，快點走吧</p>
<p begin="9102200000t" end="9113000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">艾瑪她…</p>
<p begin="9113800000t" end="9126200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="9163800000t" end="9177000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">她流血了</p>
<p begin="9182200000t" end="9199400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">耳朵的傷口裂開了</p>
<p begin="9205000000t" end="9222600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">而且發高燒</p>
<p begin="9225400000t" end="9246600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">雷不在，連艾瑪也…</p>
<p begin="9247400000t" end="9260600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">那怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="9300600000t" end="9313000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">這邊</p>
<p begin="9345800000t" end="9359000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">這邊</p>
<p begin="9366200000t" end="9390600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">人類？　　是一個女生？</p>
<p begin="9409800000t" end="9444200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">克羅妮曾經說過外面是有人類的</p>
<p begin="9445000000t" end="9461000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">她是…　　同伴？</p>
<p begin="9461800000t" end="9473000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">等一下</p>
<p begin="9490600000t" end="9502200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">你是甚麼人</p>
<p begin="9503000000t" end="9523800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">讓我們看看你的臉吧</p>
<p begin="9955200000t" end="9972000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">遊戲結束了</p>
<p begin="9985200000t" end="10012800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">夠了，你的表現不錯</p>
<p begin="10027600000t" end="10041600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">放棄吧</p>
<p begin="10157600000t" end="10177200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">不行，絕對不行</p>
<p begin="10182400000t" end="10196000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">我們約定了…</p>
<p begin="10208000000t" end="10224400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">絕對不會放棄的</p>
<p begin="10245990000t" end="10259200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">追　　是</p>
<p begin="10415200000t" end="10426800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">為何讓他跑掉</p>
<p begin="10427600000t" end="10456400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">因為吸入了煙霧，鼻子嗅不到氣味</p>
<p begin="10457200000t" end="10476800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">那就用你的眼睛去找吧</p>
<p begin="10477600000t" end="10495200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">一定會留下一些腳印</p>
<p begin="10498400000t" end="10511600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">如果還找不到他</p>
<p begin="10512400000t" end="10530000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">就去找其他小孩</p>
<p begin="10532400000t" end="10544400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">知道</p>
<p begin="10550000000t" end="10573200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">他說全部人都死光了是假的</p>
<p begin="10574000000t" end="10598400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">我猜應該還有人生存</p>
<p begin="10956800000t" end="10966000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">艾瑪？</p>
<p begin="10972000000t" end="10980800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="10990400000t" end="11020800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">艾瑪…</p>
<p begin="11042800000t" end="11063600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">是雷嗎</p>
<p begin="11114400000t" end="11135200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">是雷？你回來了嗎</p>
<p begin="11146000000t" end="11175200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">真的太好了，你終於回來了</p>
<p begin="11184800000t" end="11200800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">實在太好了</p>
<p begin="11204800000t" end="11220800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">艾瑪，你沒事就好了</p>
<p begin="11261200000t" end="11272000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">原來如此</p>
<p begin="11276000000t" end="11309200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">我們在不同的地方被救到這裡來</p>
<p begin="11321600000t" end="11353600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">戴頭巾的男人和戴頭巾的女生</p>
<p begin="11377600000t" end="11410000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">被鋪、食水和呼救用的鈴噹</p>
<p begin="11425600000t" end="11445200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">而且我們都沒有被綁起來</p>
<p begin="11451200000t" end="11480800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">從種種跡象來看，對方不是敵人</p>
<p begin="11492000000t" end="11525200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">你猜是米涅瓦先生救了我們嗎</p>
<p begin="11535600000t" end="11568400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">有可能的，即使不是他本人</p>
<p begin="11569200000t" end="11587200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">也可能是他的同伴</p>
<p begin="11626400000t" end="11635200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">來了</p>
<p begin="11729200000t" end="11740400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">太好了</p>
<p begin="11750000000t" end="11769600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">那些草藥真的很有效</p>
<p begin="11778000000t" end="11802000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">不過也不可以勉強</p>
<p begin="11802800000t" end="11823200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">如果再次暈倒，那就麻煩了</p>
<p begin="11833200000t" end="11878400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">你們竟然從農場逃跑來這裡</p>
<p begin="11882000000t" end="11899600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">現在你們安全了</p>
<p begin="11902400000t" end="11943200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">請問其他人呢？跟我一起的那群人</p>
<p begin="11946000000t" end="11962800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">他們就在那邊</p>
<p begin="11967200000t" end="12002000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">對了，我剛做好飯，一起吃吧</p>
<p begin="12110800000t" end="12120000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">請問…</p>
<p begin="12128800000t" end="12154400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">救了我的那個戴頭巾的男人</p>
<p begin="12155200000t" end="12168400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">是你的同伴嗎</p>
<p begin="12176000000t" end="12219600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">你是指孫居嗎？對，他也在那邊</p>
<p begin="12228000000t" end="12263600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">不是米涅瓦先生嗎　　米涅瓦？</p>
<p begin="12264400000t" end="12292400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">你不認識威廉米涅瓦先生嗎</p>
<p begin="12297600000t" end="12306800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">不認識</p>
<p begin="12312400000t" end="12323600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">是嗎</p>
<p begin="12366400000t" end="12375600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">請問…</p>
<p begin="12382000000t" end="12402000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">為何鬼族也會救人類</p>
<p begin="12414000000t" end="12426000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">你是說…</p>
<p begin="12611600000t" end="12624800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">原來真的是鬼族</p>
<p begin="12631600000t" end="12651200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">你和那個男人都是</p>
<p begin="12663600000t" end="12701600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">你坦白告訴我，你們為何要這麼做</p>
<p begin="12840800000t" end="12866400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">(當你許下願望)</p>
<p begin="12867200000t" end="12894000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">(月亮就灑下了影子)</p>
<p begin="12894800000t" end="12950400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">(像魔法一般的夜晚必定融化無蹤)</p>
<p begin="13058800000t" end="13084400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">(以澄澈響亮的聲音)</p>
<p begin="13085200000t" end="13111600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">(風宣布了夜色來臨)</p>
<p begin="13112400000t" end="13137600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">(藍色世界的一切)</p>
<p begin="13138400000t" end="13166800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">(都在童話裡沉睡)</p>
<p begin="13167600000t" end="13193200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">(你在半夢半醒之間)</p>
<p begin="13194000000t" end="13221200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">(張開了閉著的眼瞼)</p>
<p begin="13222000000t" end="13258000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">(比我心裡所想的)</p>
<p begin="13258800000t" end="13281200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">(還要更加朦朧)</p>
<p begin="13298000000t" end="13346800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">(如果這聲音能傳達)</p>
<p begin="13347600000t" end="13374000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">(即使得不到回應　也想在你身旁)</p>
<p begin="13374800000t" end="13406000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">(不想讓這個故事畫下句點)</p>
<p begin="13406800000t" end="13455600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">(跨越長夜而去吧)</p>
<p begin="13456400000t" end="13482800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">(跟你在一起　就再也不需要言語)</p>
<p begin="13483600000t" end="13528400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">(如今只想確認彼此的溫度)</p>
